{"title":"No.22 Bicycles Updates its Drifter Line of Gravel Bikes from Top to Bottom","link":"https://bikerumor.com/no-22-bicycles-updates-drifter-gravel-bikes-titanium/","date":1749131097000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" alt=\"(Photos / No. 22 Bicycles)\" /></p>\n<p>New York’s super flashy, boutique bicycle brand, No.22 Bicycles, has just announced a complete revamp of its Drifter line of gravel bikes. Known for their amazing work with 3D printing and the ability to prototype quickly, the Dirfter family gets new features, updated geo, more tire clearance, and new aesthetics.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line first pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-first-pic-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Drifter X</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Each No.22 is handmade in either stock or custom geometry in their Upstate New York facility. The Drifter Gravel family has three models: the Drifter X, Drifter, and Drifter Adventure. And, all of them get geo updates and more tire clearance. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line gallery 2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-2-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Drifter</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line gallery 1\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-gallery-1-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Drifter Adventure</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Both the Drifter and Drifter Adventure will get an entirely new 3D-printed yoke. Also coming this Summer from No.22’s sister brand, N0.6 Composites, a new suspension-corrected fork is included. This new fork will be available after-market, with a frame, or a complete bicycle.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Drifter X</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $6,499 (frame, fork, Ti headset, and seatmast topper)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter x\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Drifter X is a bike aimed at light gravel / all-road, and is perfectly suitable for non-competitive gravel riding, and that wider-tired “all-road” usage. The frame is said to stay “crisp” and responsive under power.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter x rear wheel\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-wheel-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter x front fender\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-front-fender-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Drifter X sports a slightly steeper seat tube angle. This allows for shorter seat stays, providing wider tire clearance. All of this, while maintaining the signature Drifter ride quality.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-topper.webp\"><img width=\"854\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-topper.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter x topper\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-topper.webp 854w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-topper-200x300.webp 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-topper-80x120.webp 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-topper-768x1151.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-fender.webp\"><img width=\"854\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-fender.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter x rear fender\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-fender.webp 854w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-fender-200x300.webp 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-fender-80x120.webp 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-x-rear-fender-768x1151.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Tire clearance: 42mm. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fork: No. 6 Composites Gravel fork, 47mm clearance.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drivetrain: 1X or 2X compatible. A Wide drivetrain is not required.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Max chainring sizes: 1x: 48T via SRAM Wide standard 2X: Tested for clearance up to 48/35 using a non-Wide SRAM crankset.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Titanium seatpost or seatmast. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>A fully internal cable routing option is available for $1,500. It includes an internally routed fork, No. 22 bespoke 3D-printed titanium stem, and titanium headset.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UDH compatible.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Drifter</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $6,199 (frame, carbon suspension-corrected fork, Ti headset, and Ti seatpost clamp)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / No. 22 Bicycles)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Drfter was designed with contemporary gravel racing in mind. It rocks a suspension-corrected rigid fork, and is said to deliver a high level of stiffness under power.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-fork-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-yoke-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Add aggressive handling and maximum tire clearance, and you’ve got an Unbound race bike. The Drifter can clear 56mm tires with 5mm of clearance by utilizing No.22’s new 3D printed yoke. Even if you want to run 2x, the frame will still clear a 45mm tire with a front derailleur. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-logo-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter rear wheel\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-rear-wheel-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The shorter chainstays and moderate reach make the Drifter the brand’s flagship gravel model, which prioritizes speed and effective power transfer.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Tire clearance: 56mm/2.2” using 1X drivetrains, 45mm with a front derailleur.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fork: No. 6 Composites suspension corrected, 430mm A-C. 47mm offset.. 61mm tire clearance.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Brakes: Rear native 160. Front 160/180mm rotor.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drivetrain: 1X or 2X compatible utilizing a Wide drivetrain.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Max chainring sizes: 1X: 46T via SRAM Wide standard 2X: 40/33 via SRAM Wide.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Seat mast: Not standard, but available as an option.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A fully internal cable routing option is available for $1,500. It includes an internally routed fork, No. 22 bespoke 3D-printed titanium stem, and titanium headset.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UDH compatible.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Drifter Adventure</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $6,499 (frame, carbon adventure fork, Ti headset, Ti seatpost clamp, and “all the bosses”)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-adventure-e1749066877331.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-adventure-e1749066877331.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line drifter adventure\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-adventure-e1749066877331.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-adventure-e1749066877331-297x188.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-adventure-e1749066877331-120x76.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-drifter-adventure-e1749066877331-768x486.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Drifter Adventure means maximum versatility. Designed to be ready for any adventure, singletrack, or bikepacking trip, it includes a plethora of bikepacking mounts, is stable when loaded, and can tackle most mild singletrack.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line adventure clean rear dropouts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-clean-rear-dropouts-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-long-chainstays-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>No.22 uses tube selection, the optional front suspension, and clearance for over a 50mm tire to give the Drifter Adventure compliance for all-day rides. It also sports a redesigned 3D printed yolk, combined with longer reach and longer chainstays.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line adventure new yoke\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-new-yoke-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages.webp\" alt=\"No.22 New Updated Drifter Gravel Bike Line adventure cages\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/No.22-New-Updated-Drifter-Gravel-Bike-Line-adventure-cages-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All of this positions the rider comfortably when the going gets rough.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Tire clearance: 52mm using 1X drivetrains, 45mm with a front derailleur.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fork: No. 6 Composites Adventure fork.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Brakes: Rear native 160. Front 140/160mm rotor.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drivetrain: 1X or 2X compatible utilizing a Wide drivetrain.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Max chainring sizes: 48T via SRAM Wide standard / 2X: 40/33 via SRAM Wide. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Multiple mounting points are standard: 3 bottle cages, a bento box, and fork mounts.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A fully internal cable routing option is available for $1,500. It includes an internally routed fork, No. 22 bespoke 3D-printed titanium stem, and titanium headset.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UDH compatible.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://22bicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">22Bicycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/no-22-bicycles-updates-drifter-gravel-bikes-titanium/\">No.22 Bicycles Updates its Drifter Line of Gravel Bikes from Top to Bottom</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ae11956af218c2c2b9f358bd8d1c293e8e0d0875160f0ebf38ca1220d2769cbf","category":"Cycling"}